315#$#O for a Closer Walk!#$#0#$##$##$##$#Verse 1@%O for a closer walk with God!@%A calm and heavenly frame,@%A light to shine upon the road@%That leads me to the Lamb.@$Verse 2@%Return, O holy Dove! return,@%Sweet messenger of rest;@%I hate the sins that made Thee mourn,@%And drove Thee from my breast.@$Verse 3@%What peaceful hours I once enjoyed!@%How sweet their memory still!@%But they have left an aching void@%The world can never fill.@$Verse 4@%The dearest idol I have known,@%Whate'er that idol be,@%Help me to tear it from Thy throne,@%And worship only Thee.#$##$#left#$#
